#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmplot; is a mathematical function plotter by &kde;. It has a powerful "
"built-in parser. You can plot different functions simultaneously and combine "
"them to build new functions."
msgstr ""
"&kmplot; je &kde; risalnik matematičnih funkcij. Ima zmogljiv vgrajen "
"razčlenjevalec. Hkrati lahko narišete različne funkcije in jih kombinirate, "
"da ustvarite nove funkcije."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Examples</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Primeri</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Examples</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Primeri</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmplot; supports several different types of plots:"
msgstr "&kmplot; podpira več različnih vrst ploskev:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Explicit cartesian plots of the form y = f(x)."
msgstr "Eksplicitni kartezični diagrami oblike y = f(x)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Parametric plots, where the x and y components are specified as functions of "
"an independent variable."
msgstr ""
"Parametrične ploskve, kjer sta komponenti x in y določeni kot funkciji "
"neodvisne spremenljivke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "Polar plots of the form r = r(&thgr;)."
msgstr "Polarne grafike oblike r = r(&thgr;)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Implicit plots, where the x and y coordinates are related by an expression."
msgstr "Implicitni izrisi, kjer sta koordinati x in y povezani z izrazom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "Explicit differential plots."
msgstr "Eksplicitne diferencialne ploskve."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmplot; also provides some numerical and visual features like:"
msgstr "&kmplot; ponuja tudi nekaj numeričnih in vizualnih funkcij, kot so:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filling and calculating the area between the plot and the first axis."
msgstr "Zapolnitev in izračun površine med parcelo in prvo osjo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finding maximum and minimum values."
msgstr "Iskanje največjih in najmanjših vrednosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changing function parameters dynamically."
msgstr "Dinamično spreminjanje funkcijskih parametrov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plotting derivatives and integral functions."
msgstr "Risanje odvodov in integralnih funkcij."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These features help in learning the relationship between mathematical "
"functions and their graphical representation in a coordinate system."
msgstr ""
"Te funkcije pomagajo pri učenju odnosa med matematičnimi funkcijami in "
"njihovo grafično predstavitvijo v koordinatnem sistemu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "First Steps With &kmplot;"
msgstr "Prvi koraki z &kmplot;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Simple Function Plot"
msgstr "Enostavna grafična funkcija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the sidebar on the left, there is the <guibutton>Create</guibutton> "
"button with a drop down menu for creating new plots. Click on it, and select "
"<guilabel>Cartesian Plot</guilabel>. The text box for editing the current "
"equation will be focused. Replace the default text with <screen><userinput>y "
"= x^2</userinput></screen> and press &Enter;. This will draw the plot of y = "
"x<superscript>2</superscript> in the coordinate system. Clicking on the "
"<guibutton>Create</guibutton> button again, select <guilabel>Cartesian Plot</"
"guilabel>, and this time enter the text <screen><userinput>y = 5sin(x)</"
"userinput></screen> to get another plot."
msgstr ""
"V stranski vrstici na levi je gumb <guibutton>Ustvari</guibutton> s spustnim "
"menijem za ustvarjanje novih risb. Kliknite nanj in izberite "
"<guilabel>Kartezijski izris</guilabel>. Besedilno polje za urejanje trenutne "
"enačbe bo osredotočeno. Zamenjajte privzeto besedilo z <screen><userinput>y "
"= x^2</userinput></screen> in pritisnite &Enter;. To bo narisalo graf y = "
"x<superscript>2</superscript> v koordinatnem sistemu. S ponovnim klikom na "
"gumb <guibutton>Ustvari</guibutton> izberite <guilabel>Kartezijski izris</"
"guilabel> in tokrat vnesite besedilo <screen><userinput>y = 5sin(x)</"
"userinput></screen > dobiti drugo parcelo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Drag and drop the item <userinput>y = 5sin(x)</userinput> in the left "
"sidebar to clone the plot. Replace <userinput>sin</userinput> with "
"<userinput>cos</userinput> to get the cosine plot of the same color."
msgstr ""
"Povlecite in spustite element <userinput>y = 5sin(x)</userinput> v levi "
"stranski vrstici, da klonirate graf. Zamenjajte <userinput>sin</userinput> z "
"<userinput>cos</userinput>, da dobite graf kosinusa enake barve."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on one of the lines you have just plotted. Now the crosshair becomes "
"the color of the current plot and is attached to the it. You can use the "
"mouse to move the crosshair along the plot. In the status bar at the bottom "
"of the window the coordinates of the current position is displayed. Note "
"that if the plot touches the horizontal axis the root will be displayed in "
"the status bar, too."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite eno od črt, ki ste jih pravkar narisali. Zdaj postane križec barve "
"trenutne risbe in je pritrjen nanjo. Z miško lahko premikate križec po "
"risbi. V statusni vrstici na dnu okna so prikazane koordinate trenutnega "
"položaja. Upoštevajte, da če se graf dotika vodoravne osi, bo koren prikazan "
"tudi v statusni vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click the mouse again and the crosshair will be detached from the plot."
msgstr "Ponovno kliknite miško in križec se bo ločil od risbe."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit Properties"
msgstr "Uredi lastnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let us make some changes to the function and change the color of the plot."
msgstr "Naredimo nekaj sprememb v funkciji in spremenimo barvo risbe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Functions</guilabel> sidebar lists all the functions that you "
"have plotted. If <guilabel>y = x^2</guilabel> isn't already selected, select "
"it. Here you have access to a lot of options. Let us rename the function and "
"move the plot 5 units down. Change the function equation to "
"<screen><userinput>parabola(x) = x^2 - 5</userinput></screen> and hit enter. "
"To select another color for the plot, click the <guilabel>Color</guilabel> "
"button in the section <guilabel>Appearance</guilabel> at the bottom of the "
"Functions sidebar and select a new color."
msgstr ""
"Stranska vrstica <guilabel>Funkcije</guilabel> navaja vse funkcije, ki ste "
"jih izrisali. Če <guilabel>y = x^2</guilabel> še ni izbran, ga izberite. "
"Tukaj imate dostop do številnih možnosti. Preimenujmo funkcijo in premaknimo "
"graf 5 enot navzdol. Enačbo funkcije spremenite v "
"<screen><userinput>parabola(x) = x^2 - 5</userinput></screen> in pritisnite "
"tipko enter. Če želite izbrati drugo barvo za izris, kliknite gumb "
"<guilabel>Barva</guilabel> v razdelku <guilabel>Videz</guilabel> na dnu "
"stranske vrstice s funkcijami in izberite novo barvo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All changes can be undone via <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Vse spremembe je mogoče razveljaviti prek <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Razveljavi</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kmplot;"
msgstr "Uporaba &kmplot;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmplot; deals with several different types of functions, which can be "
"written in function form or as an equation:"
msgstr ""
"&kmplot; obravnava več različnih vrst funkcij, ki jih lahko zapišemo v "
"funkcijski obliki ali kot enačbo:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cartesian plots can either be written as &eg; <quote>y = x^2</quote>, where "
"x has to be used as the variable; or as &eg; <quote>f(a) = a^2</quote>, "
"where the name of the variable is arbitrary."
msgstr ""
"Kartezične ploskve lahko zapišemo kot &eg; <quote>y = x^2</quote>, kjer je "
"treba x uporabiti kot spremenljivko; ali kot &eg; <quote>f(a) = a^2</quote>, "
"kjer je ime spremenljivke poljubno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Parametric plots are similar to Cartesian plots. The x and y coordinates can "
"be entered as equations in t, &eg; <quote>x = sin(t)</quote>, <quote>y = "
"cos(t)</quote>, or as functions, &eg; <quote>f_x(s) = sin(s)</quote>, "
"<quote>f_y(s) = cos(s)</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Parametrične ploskve so podobne kartezičnim grafom. Koordinate x in y lahko "
"vnesete kot enačbe v t, &eg; <quote>x = sin(t)</quote>, <quote>y = cos(t)</"
"quote> ali kot funkcije, &eg; <quote>f_x(s) = sin(s)</quote>, <quote>f_y(s) "
"= cos(s)</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Polar plots are also similar to Cartesian plots. They can be either be "
"entered as an equation in &thgr;, &eg; <quote>r = &thgr;</quote>, or as a "
"function, &eg; <quote>f(x) = x</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Polarne ploskve so prav tako podobne kartezičnim grafom. Lahko jih bodisi "
"vnesete kot enačbo v &thgr;, &eg; <quote>r = &thgr;</quote> ali kot "
"funkcija, &eg; <quote>f(x) = x</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For implicit plots, the name of the function is entered separately from the "
"expression relating the x and y coordinates. If the x and y variables are "
"specified via the function name (by entering &eg;<quote>f(a,b)</quote> as "
"the function name), then these variables will be used. Otherwise, the "
"letters x and y will be used for the variables."
msgstr ""
"Pri implicitnih grafih se ime funkcije vnese ločeno od izraza, ki se nanaša "
"na koordinate x in y. Če sta spremenljivki x in y podani prek imena funkcije "
"(z vnosom &eg;<quote>f(a,b)</quote> kot ime funkcije), bosta uporabljeni ti "
"spremenljivki. V nasprotnem primeru bosta za spremenljivke uporabljeni črki "
"x in y."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Explicit differential plots are differential equations whereby the highest "
"derivative is given in terms of the lower derivatives. Differentiation is "
"denoted by a prime ('). In function form, the equation will look like "
"<quote>f''(x) = f' &minus; f</quote>. In equation form, it will look like "
"<quote>y'' = y' &minus; y</quote>. Note that in both cases, the <quote>(x)</"
"quote> part is not added to the lower order differential terms (so you would "
"enter <quote>f'(x) = &minus;f</quote> and not <quote>f'(x) = &minus;f(x)</"
"quote>)."
msgstr ""
"Eksplicitni diferencialni diagrami so diferencialne enačbe, pri katerih je "
"najvišji odvod podan v smislu nižjih odvodov. Diferenciacijo označujemo s "
"praštevilo ('). V obliki funkcije bo enačba videti kot <quote>f''(x) = f' "
"&minus; f</quote>. V obliki enačbe bo videti kot <quote>y'' = y' &minus; y</"
"quote>. Upoštevajte, da v obeh primerih del <quote>(x)</quote> ni dodan "
"diferencialnim členom nižjega reda (zato bi vnesli <quote>f'(x) = &minus;f</"
"quote> in ne <quote>f'(x) = &minus;f(x)</quote>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All the equation entry boxes come with a button on the right. Clicking this "
"invokes the advanced <guilabel>Equation Editor</guilabel> dialog, which "
"provides:"
msgstr ""
"Vsa polja za vnos enačb imajo gumb na desni. S klikom na to se odpre "
"napredno pogovorno okno <guilabel>Urejevalnik enačb</guilabel>, ki ponuja:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A variety of mathematical symbols that can be used in equations, but aren't "
"found on normal keyboards."
msgstr ""
"Različni matematični simboli, ki jih je mogoče uporabiti v enačbah, vendar "
"jih ni na običajnih tipkovnicah."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "The list of user constants and a button for editing them."
msgstr "Seznam uporabniških konstant in gumb za njihovo urejanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The list of predefined functions. Note that if you have text already "
"selected, it will be used as the function argument when a function is "
"inserted. For example, if <quote>1 + x</quote> is selected in the equation "
"<quote>y = 1 + x</quote>, and the sine function is chosen, then the equation "
"will become <quote> y = sin(1+x)</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Seznam vnaprej določenih funkcij. Upoštevajte, da če ste besedilo že "
"izbrali, bo uporabljeno kot argument funkcije, ko je funkcija vstavljena. Na "
"primer, če je izbran <quote>1 + x</quote> v enačbi <quote>y = 1 + x</quote> "
"in je izbrana sinusna funkcija, bo enačba postala <quote> y = sin (1+x)</"
"quote>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here is a screenshot of the &kmplot; welcome window"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona &kmplot; pozdravno okno"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid "Function Types"
msgstr "Vrste funkcij"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cartesian Functions"
msgstr "Kartezične funkcije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To enter an explicit function (&ie;, a function in the form y=f(x)) into "
"&kmplot;, just enter it in the following form: "
"<screen><userinput><replaceable>f</replaceable>(<replaceable>x</"
"replaceable>) = <replaceable>expression</replaceable></userinput></screen> "
"where:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite vnesti eksplicitno funkcijo (&ie; funkcijo v obliki y=f(x)) v "
"&kmplot;, jo preprosto vnesite v naslednji obliki: "
"<screen><userinput><replaceable>f</replaceable>(<replaceable >x</"
"replaceable>) = <replaceable>izraz</replaceable></userinput></screen> kjer "
"je:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<replaceable>f</replaceable> is the name of the function, and can be any "
"string of letters and numbers."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>f</replaceable> je ime funkcije in je lahko poljuben niz črk in "
"številk."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<replaceable>x</replaceable> is the horizontal coordinate, to be used in the "
"expression following the equals sign. It is a dummy variable, so you can use "
"any variable name you like to achieve the same effect."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>x</replaceable> je vodoravna koordinata, ki jo je treba "
"uporabiti v izrazu za znakom enačaja. To je navidezna spremenljivka, zato "
"lahko uporabite poljubno ime spremenljivke, da dosežete enak učinek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<replaceable>expression</replaceable> is the expression to be plotted, given "
"in the appropriate syntax for &kmplot;. See <xref linkend=\"math-syntax\"/>."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>expression</replaceable> je izraz, ki ga je treba narisati, "
"podan v ustrezni sintaksi za &kmplot;. Glejte <xref linkend=\"math-syntax\"/"
">."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parametric Functions"
msgstr "Parametrične funkcije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Parametric functions are those in which the x and y coordinates are defined "
"by separate functions of another variable, often called t. To enter a "
"parametric function in &kmplot;, follow the procedure as for a Cartesian "
"function for each of the x and y functions. As with Cartesian functions, you "
"may use any variable name you wish for the parameter."
msgstr ""
"Parametrične funkcije so tiste, pri katerih sta koordinati x in y definirani "
"z ločenima funkcijama druge spremenljivke, ki se pogosto imenuje t. Če "
"želite v &kmplot; vnesti parametrično funkcijo, sledite postopku kot za "
"kartezično funkcijo za vsako od funkcij x in y. Tako kot pri kartezičnih "
"funkcijah lahko tudi za parameter uporabite poljubno ime spremenljivke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As an example, suppose you want to draw a circle, which has parametric "
"equations x = sin(t), y = cos(t). After creating a parametric plot, enter "
"the appropriate equations in the x and y boxes, &ie;, "
"<userinput>f_x(t)=sin(t)</userinput> and <userinput>f_y(t)=cos(t)</"
"userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Recimo, da želite narisati krog, ki ima parametrične enačbe x = sin(t), y = "
"cos(t). Ko ustvarite parametrični diagram, vnesite ustrezne enačbe v polji x "
"in y, &ie;, <userinput>f_x(t)=sin(t)</userinput> in "
"<userinput>f_y(t)=cos(t)</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:251 index.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can set some further options for the plot in the function editor:"
msgstr ""
"V urejevalniku funkcij lahko nastavite nekaj dodatnih možnosti za izris:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid "Min:"
msgstr "Min:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid "Max:"
msgstr "Max:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These options control the range of the parameter t for which the function is "
"plotted."
msgstr ""
"Te možnosti nadzorujejo obseg parametra t, za katerega je funkcija narisana."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid "Functions in Polar Coordinates"
msgstr "Funkcije v polarnih koordinatah"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Polar coordinates represent a point by its distance from the origin (usually "
"called r), and the angle a line from the origin to the point makes with the "
"horizontal axis (usually represented by &thgr; the Greek letter theta). To "
"enter functions in polar coordinates, click the <guibutton>Create</"
"guibutton> button and select <guilabel>Polar Plot</guilabel> from the list. "
"In the definition box, complete the function definition, including the name "
"of the theta variable you want to use, &eg;, to draw the Archimedes' spiral "
"r = &thgr;, enter: <screen><userinput>r(&thgr;) = &thgr;</userinput></"
"screen> Note that you can use any name for the theta variable, so "
"<quote>r(t) = t</quote> or <quote>f(x) = x</quote> will produce exactly the "
"same output."
msgstr ""
"Polarne koordinate predstavljajo točko z njeno oddaljenostjo od izhodišča "
"(običajno imenovano r) in kotom, ki ga črta od izhodišča do točke tvori z "
"vodoravno osjo (običajno predstavljeno z &thgr; grško črko theta). Za vnos "
"funkcij v polarnih koordinatah kliknite gumb <guibutton>Ustvari</guibutton> "
"in s seznama izberite <guilabel>Polarni izris</guilabel>. V polju za "
"definicijo dokončajte definicijo funkcije, vključno z imenom theta "
"spremenljivke, ki jo želite uporabiti, &eg;, da narišete Arhimedovo spiralo "
"r = &thgr;, vnesite: <screen><userinput>r(&thgr;) = &thgr;</userinput></"
"screen> Upoštevajte, da lahko uporabite poljubno ime za spremenljivko theta, "
"torej <quote>r(t) = t</quote> ali <quote>f(x) = x</quote> bo ustvaril "
"popolnoma enak izhod."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid "Implicit Functions"
msgstr "Implicitne funkcije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An implicit expression relates the x and y coordinates as an equality. To "
"create a circle, for example, click the <guibutton>Create</guibutton> button "
"and select <guilabel>Implicit Plot</guilabel> from the list. Then, enter "
"into the equation box (below the function name box) the following:"
msgstr ""
"Implicitni izraz povezuje koordinate x in y kot enakost. Če želite na primer "
"ustvariti krog, kliknite gumb <guibutton>Ustvari</guibutton> in s seznama "
"izberite <guilabel>Implicitni izris</guilabel>. Nato v polje z enačbo (pod "
"poljem z imenom funkcije) vnesite naslednje:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>x^2 + y^2 = 25</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput>x^2 y^2 = 25</userinput>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid "Differential Functions"
msgstr "Diferencialne funkcije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmplot; can plot explicit differential equations. These are equations of "
"the form y<superscript>(n)</superscript> = F(x,y',y'',...,"
"y<superscript>(n&minus;1)</superscript>), where y<superscript>k</"
"superscript> is the k<superscript>th</superscript> derivative of y(x). "
"&kmplot; can only interpret the derivative order as the number of primes "
"following the function name. To draw a sinusoidal curve, for example, you "
"would use the differential equation <userinput>y'' = &minus; y</userinput> "
"or <userinput>f''(x) = −f</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"&kmplot; zna narisati eksplicitne diferencialne enačbe. To so enačbe v "
"obliki y<superscript>(n)</superscript> = F(x,y',y'',...,"
"y<superscript>(n&minus;1)</superscript>), kjer je y <superscript>k</"
"superscript> je k<superscript>th</superscript> izpeljanka y(x). &kmplot; "
"lahko interpretira vrstni red izpeljave le kot število praštevil, ki sledijo "
"imenu funkcije. Za risanje sinusne krivulje bi na primer uporabili "
"diferencialno enačbo <userinput>y'' = &minus; y</userinput> ali "
"<userinput>f''(x) = −f</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"However, a differential equation on its own isn't enough to determine a "
"plot. Each curve in the diagram is generated by a combination of the "
"differential equation and the initial conditions. You can edit the initial "
"conditions by clicking on the <guilabel>Initial Conditions</guilabel> tab "
"when a differential equation is selected. The number of columns provided for "
"editing the initial conditions is dependent on the order of the differential "
"equation."
msgstr ""
"Vendar diferencialna enačba sama po sebi ni dovolj za določitev grafa. Vsaka "
"krivulja v diagramu je ustvarjena s kombinacijo diferencialne enačbe in "
"začetnih pogojev. Začetne pogoje lahko uredite s klikom na zavihek "
"<guilabel>Začetni pogoji</guilabel>, ko je izbrana diferencialna enačba. "
"Število stolpcev, ki so na voljo za urejanje začetnih pogojev, je odvisno od "
"vrstnega reda diferencialne enačbe."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid "Step:"
msgstr "Korak:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The step value in the precision box is used in numerically solving the "
"differential equation (using the Runge Kutta method). Its value is the "
"maximum step size used; a smaller step size may be used if part of the "
"differential plot is zoomed in close enough."
msgstr ""
"Vrednost koraka v polju za natančnost se uporablja pri numeričnem reševanju "
"diferencialne enačbe (z uporabo metode Runge Kutta). Njegova vrednost je "
"največja uporabljena velikost koraka; manjša velikost koraka se lahko "
"uporabi, če je del diferencialnega grafa dovolj povečan."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid "Combining Functions"
msgstr "Združevanje funkcij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:319
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Functions can be combined to produce new ones. Simply enter the functions "
"after the equals sign in an expression as if the functions were variables. "
"For example, if you have defined functions f(x) and g(x), you can plot the "
"sum of f and g with:"
msgstr ""
"Funkcije je mogoče združiti za ustvarjanje novih. Preprosto vnesite funkcije "
"za znakom enačaja v izraz, kot da bi bile funkcije spremenljivke. Na primer, "
"če ste definirali funkciji f(x) in g(x), lahko narišete vsoto f in g z:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>sum(x) = f(x) + g(x)</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput>vsota(x) = f(x) g(x)</userinput>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changing the appearance of functions"
msgstr "Spreminjanje videza funkcij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the appearance of a function's graph on the main plot window, "
"select the function in the <guilabel>Functions</guilabel> sidebar. You can "
"change the plot's line width, color and many other aspects by clicking on "
"the <guibutton>Color:</guibutton> or <guibutton>Advanced...</guibutton> "
"button at the bottom of the section <guilabel>Appearance</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti videz grafa funkcije v glavnem oknu grafa, izberite "
"funkcijo v stranski vrstici <guilabel>Funkcije</guilabel>. S klikom na gumb "
"<guibutton>Barva:</guibutton> ali <guibutton>Napredno...</guibutton> na dnu "
"razdelka <guilabel>Videz</guilabel> lahko spremenite širino črte izrisa, "
"barvo in številne druge vidike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:337
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are editing a Cartesian function, the function editor will have three "
"tabs. In the first one you specify the equation of the function. The "
"<guilabel>Derivatives</guilabel> tab lets you draw the first and second "
"derivative to the function. With the <guilabel>Integral</guilabel> tab you "
"can draw the integral of the function."
msgstr ""
"Če urejate kartezično funkcijo, bo imel urejevalnik funkcij tri zavihke. V "
"prvem določite enačbo funkcije. Zavihek <guilabel>Izpeljanke</guilabel> vam "
"omogoča, da narišete prvi in drugi odvod v funkciji. Z zavihkom "
"<guilabel>Integral</guilabel> lahko narišete integral funkcije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid "Popup menu"
msgstr "Pojavni meni"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Graph right-click popup menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pojavni meni desnega klika grafa</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Graph right-click popup menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pojavni meni desnega klika grafa</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:359
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When right-clicking on a plot function or a single-point parametric plot "
"function a popup menu will appear. In the menu there are five items "
"available:"
msgstr ""
"Ko z desno miškino tipko kliknete funkcijo izrisa ali funkcijo "
"parametričnega izrisa z eno točko, se prikaže pojavni meni. V meniju je na "
"voljo pet elementov:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit"
msgstr "Uredi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selects the function in the <guilabel>Functions</guilabel> sidebar for "
"editing."
msgstr ""
"Izbere funkcijo v stranski vrstici <guilabel>Funkcije</guilabel> za urejanje."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide"
msgstr "Skrij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hides the selected graph. Other plots of the graph's function will still be "
"shown."
msgstr ""
"Skrije izbrani graf. Drugi diagrami funkcije grafa bodo še vedno prikazani."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:380
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove"
msgstr "Odstrani"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removes the function. All its graphs will disappear."
msgstr "Odstrani funkcijo. Vsi njeni grafi bodo izginili."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid "Animate Plot..."
msgstr "Animiraj zaplet ..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:390
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays the <guilabel>Parameter Animator</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr "Prikaže pogovorno okno <guilabel>Animator parametrov</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calculator"
msgstr "Kalkulator"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:397 index.docbook:1342
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the <guilabel>Calculator</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr "Odpre pogovorno okno <guilabel>Kalkulator</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Depending on the plot type, there will also be up to five tools available:"
msgstr "Odvisno od vrste ploskve bo na voljo tudi do pet orodij:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy (x, y)"
msgstr "Kopiraj (x, y)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:409
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copies the current value on the plot to the system clipboard. This tool can "
"be useful for creating tables of function values outside of &kmplot;."
msgstr ""
"Kopira trenutno vrednost na grafu v sistemsko odložišče. To orodje je lahko "
"uporabno za ustvarjanje tabel funkcijskih vrednosti zunaj &kmplot;."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy Root Value"
msgstr "Kopiraj korensko vrednost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copies the root <literal>x</literal> value to the system clipboard. Only up "
"to the first five digits after the decimal point can be copied. Use some "
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computer_algebra_system"
"\">computer algebra system</ulink> to determine this root with arbitrary "
"precision. This tool is only available when the current tracking position is "
"close to a root."
msgstr ""
"Kopira korensko vrednost <literal>x</literal> v sistemsko odložišče. "
"Kopirate lahko le do prvih pet števk za decimalno vejico. Uporabite <ulink "
"url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computer_algebra_system\">sistem "
"računalniške algebre</ulink>, da določite ta koren s poljubno natančnostjo. "
"To orodje je na voljo le, če je trenutni položaj sledenja blizu korena."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:428
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plot Area..."
msgstr "Območje parcele..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:431
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the minimum and maximum horizontal values for the graph in the new "
"dialog that appears. Calculates the integral and draws the area between the "
"graph and the horizontal axis in the selected range in the color of the "
"graph."
msgstr ""
"V novem pogovornem oknu, ki se prikaže, izberite najmanjšo in največjo "
"vodoravno vrednost za graf. Izračuna integral in nariše območje med grafom "
"in vodoravno osjo v izbranem območju v barvi grafa."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:439
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find Minimum..."
msgstr "Najdi minimum..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Find the minimum value of the graph in a specified range. The selected graph "
"will be highlighted in the dialog that appears. Enter the lower and upper "
"boundaries of the region in which you want to search for a minimum."
msgstr ""
"Poiščite najmanjšo vrednost grafa v določenem območju. Izbrani graf bo "
"označen v pogovornem oknu, ki se prikaže. Vnesite spodnjo in zgornjo mejo "
"regije, v kateri želite iskati minimum."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:448
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note: You can also tell the plot to visually show the extreme points in the "
"<guilabel>Plot Appearance</guilabel> dialog, accessible in the "
"<guilabel>Functions</guilabel> sidebar by clicking on <guibutton>Advanced..."
"</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Opomba: grafu lahko tudi naročite, naj vizualno prikaže skrajne točke v "
"pogovornem oknu <guilabel>Videz grafa</guilabel>, ki je dostopen v stranski "
"vrstici <guilabel>Funkcije</guilabel> s klikom na <guibutton>Napredno...</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find Maximum..."
msgstr "Najdi maximum..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the same as <guimenuitem>Find Minimum...</guimenuitem> above, but "
"finds the maximum value instead of the minimum value."
msgstr ""
"To je enako kot <guimenuitem>Poišči minimum...</guimenuitem> zgoraj, vendar "
"najde največjo vrednost namesto najmanjše vrednosti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &kmplot;"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje &kmplot;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To access the &kmplot; configuration dialog, select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kmplot;...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. The settings for "
"<guimenuitem>Constants...</guimenuitem> can only be changed from the "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu and the <guimenuitem>Coordinate System...</"
"guimenuitem> only from the <guimenu>View</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do &kmplot; konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"&kmplot;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menijski element. Nastavitve za "
"<guimenuitem>Konstante ...</guimenuitem> lahko spremenite le v meniju "
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> in <guimenuitem>Koordinatni sistem...</guimenuitem> "
"samo v <guimenu>Pogledu </guimenu> meni."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:477
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Configuration"
msgstr "Splošna konfiguracija"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Screenshot of the General Settings dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna s splošnimi nastavitvami</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Screenshot of the General Settings dialog</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna s splošnimi nastavitvami</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can set global settings which automatic will be saved when you exit "
"&kmplot;. You can set angle-mode (radians and degrees), zoom in and zoom out "
"factors for zooming using &Ctrl; with mouse wheel or the <link linkend=\"a-"
"view-menu\">corresponding menu items</link>, and whether to show advanced "
"plot tracing."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko nastavite globalne nastavitve, ki se samodejno shranijo, ko "
"zapustite &kmplot;. Z &Ctrl; z miškinim koleščkom ali <link linkend=\"a-view-"
"menu\">ustreznimi elementi menija</link> in ali prikazati napredno sledenje "
"izrisu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid "Diagram Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija diagrama"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:498
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Screenshot of the Diagram Appearance dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna Videz diagrama</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Screenshot of the Diagram Appearance dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna Videz diagrama</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can set the <guilabel>Grid Style</guilabel> to one of four options:"
msgstr ""
"Nastavite lahko <guilabel>Slog mreže</guilabel> na eno od štirih možnosti:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:513
#, no-c-format
msgid "None"
msgstr "Nič"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:515
#, no-c-format
msgid "No gridlines are drawn on the plot area."
msgstr "Na območju risbe ni narisana nobena mrežna črta."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:520
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lines"
msgstr "Vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:522
#, no-c-format
msgid "Straight lines form a grid of squares on the plot area."
msgstr "Ravne črte tvorijo mrežo kvadratov na območju ploskve."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:527
#, no-c-format
msgid "Crosses"
msgstr "Križi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:529
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Crosses are drawn to indicate points where x and y have integer values "
"(&eg;, (1,1), (4,2) &etc;)."
msgstr ""
"Narisani so križci, ki označujejo točke, kjer imata x in y celoštevilske "
"vrednosti (&eg; (1,1), (4,2) &etc;)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:535
#, no-c-format
msgid "Polar"
msgstr "Polaren"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lines of constant radius and of constant angle are drawn on the plot area."
msgstr ""
"Na površino ploskve so narisane črte s konstantnim radijem in s konstantnim "
"kotom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:544
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other options for the diagram appearance can also be configured:"
msgstr "Konfigurirate lahko tudi druge možnosti za videz diagrama:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid "Axis Labels"
msgstr "Oznake osi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:549
#, no-c-format
msgid "This section sets labels for the horizontal and vertical axes."
msgstr "Ta razdelek nastavi oznake za vodoravno in navpično os."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:554
#, no-c-format
msgid "Axis widths:"
msgstr "Širine osi:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:556
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sets the width of the lines representing the axes."
msgstr "Nastavi širino črt, ki predstavljajo osi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid "Line width:"
msgstr "Širina črte:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:563
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sets the width of the lines used for drawing the grid."
msgstr "Nastavi širino črt, ki se uporabljajo za risanje mreže."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:568
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tic width:"
msgstr "Tic širina:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:570
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sets the width of the lines representing tics on the axes."
msgstr "Nastavi širino črt, ki predstavljajo tike na oseh."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:575
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tic length:"
msgstr "Tic dolžina:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:577
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sets the length of the lines representing tics on the axes."
msgstr "Nastavi dolžino črt, ki predstavljajo tike na oseh."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:582
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show labels"
msgstr "Pokaži oznake"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:584
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, the names of the axes are shown on the plot and the axes' tics "
"are labeled."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, so imena osi prikazana na grafu in oznake osi so označene."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:589
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show axes"
msgstr "Pokaži osi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:591
#, no-c-format
msgid "If checked, the axes are visible."
msgstr "Če je označeno, so osi vidne."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:596
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show arrows"
msgstr "Prikaži puščice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:598
#, no-c-format
msgid "If checked, the axes are displayed with arrows at their ends."
msgstr "Če je označeno, so osi prikazane s puščicami na koncih."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:608
#, no-c-format
