msgid "&pgr;"
msgstr "&pgr;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:894
#, no-c-format
msgid "Constants representing &pgr; (3.14159...)."
msgstr "Konstante, ki predstavljajo &pgr; (3,14159...)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:899
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>e</term>"
msgstr "<term>e</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:901
#, no-c-format
msgid "Constant representing Euler's Number e (2.71828...)."
msgstr "Konstanta, ki predstavlja Eulerjevo število e (2,71828 ...)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:910
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extensions"
msgstr "Razširitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:911
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An extension for a function is specified by entering a semicolon, followed "
"by the extension, after the function definition. The extension can be "
"entered by using the &DBus; method <quote><methodname>parser addFunction</"
"methodname></quote>. None of the extensions are available for parametric "
"functions but N and D[a,b] work for polar functions too. For example: "
"<screen>\n"
"                        <userinput>\n"
"                                f(x)=x^2; A1\n"
"                        </userinput>\n"
"                </screen> will show the graph y=x<superscript>2</"
"superscript> with its first derivative. Supported extensions are described "
"below:"
msgstr ""
"Pripono za funkcijo določite tako, da za definicijo funkcije vnesete "
"podpičje, ki mu sledi razširitev. Končnico lahko vnesete z &DBus; metoda "
"<quote><methodname>parser addFunction</methodname></quote>. Nobena od "
"razširitev ni na voljo za parametrične funkcije, vendar N in D[a,b] delujeta "
"tudi za polarne funkcije. Na primer: <screen>\n"
"                         <userinput>\n"
"                                 f(x)=x^2; A1\n"
"                         </userinput>\n"
"                 </screen> bo prikazal graf y=x<superscript>2</superscript> "
"s prvim odvodom. Podprte razširitve so opisane spodaj:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:919
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>N</term>"
msgstr "<term>N</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:921
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The function will be stored but not be drawn. It can be used like any other "
"user-defined or predefined function."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija bo shranjena, vendar ne bo narisana. Uporablja se lahko kot katera "
"koli druga uporabniško določena ali vnaprej določena funkcija."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:928
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>A1</term>"
msgstr "<term>A1</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:930
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The graph of the derivative of the function will be drawn additionally with "
"the same color but less line width."
msgstr ""
"Graf odvoda funkcije bo dodatno narisan z isto barvo, vendar z manjšo črto."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:937
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>A2</term>"
msgstr "<term>A2</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:939
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The graph of the second derivative of the function will be drawn "
"additionally with the same color but less line width."
msgstr ""
"Graf drugega odvoda funkcije bo dodatno narisan z isto barvo, vendar z "
"manjšo širino črte."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:946
#, no-c-format
msgid "D[a,b]"
msgstr "D[a,b]"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:948
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sets the domain for which the function will be displayed."
msgstr "Nastavi domeno, za katero bo prikazana funkcija."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:954
#, no-c-format
msgid "P[a{,b...}]"
msgstr "P[a{,b...}]"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:956
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Give a set of values of a group parameter for which the function should be "
"displayed. For example: <userinput>f(x,k)=k*x;P[1,2,3]</userinput> will plot "
"the functions f(x)=x, f(x)=2*x and f(x)=3*x. You can also use functions as "
"the arguments to the P option."
msgstr ""
"Podajte nabor vrednosti skupinskega parametra, za katerega naj bo prikazana "
"funkcija. Na primer: <userinput>f(x,k)=k*x;P[1,2,3]</userinput> bo izrisal "
"funkcije f(x)=x, f(x)=2*x in f (x)=3*x. Funkcije lahko uporabite tudi kot "
"argumente možnosti P."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:966
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please note that you can do all of these operations by editing the items in "
"the <guilabel>Derivatives</guilabel> tab, the <guilabel>Custom plot range</"
"guilabel> section and the <guilabel>Parameters</guilabel> section in the "
"<guilabel>Functions</guilabel> sidebar too."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da lahko vse te operacije izvedete tako, da uredite elemente na "
"zavihku <guilabel>Izpeljanke</guilabel>, razdelku <guilabel>Razpon izrisa po "
"meri</guilabel> in razdelku <guilabel>Parametri</guilabel> v tudi stransko "
"vrstico <guilabel>Funkcije</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:972
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mathematical Syntax"
msgstr "Matematična sintaksa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:973
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmplot; uses a common way of expressing mathematical functions, so you "
"should have no trouble working it out. The operators &kmplot; understands "
"are, in order of decreasing precedence:"
msgstr ""
"&kmplot; uporablja običajen način izražanja matematičnih funkcij, tako da ne "
"bi smeli imeti težav pri izdelavi. Operaterja &kmplot; razume, so po "
"padajočem vrstnem redu:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:979
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>^</term>"
msgstr "<term>^</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:980
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The caret symbol performs exponentiation. &eg;, <userinput>2^4</userinput> "
"returns 16."
msgstr ""
"Simbol kazalke izvaja potenciranje. &eg;, <userinput>2^4</userinput> vrne 16."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:986
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>*</term>"
msgstr "<term>*</term>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:987
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>/</term>"
msgstr "<term>/</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:989
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The asterisk and slash symbols perform multiplication and division . &eg;, "
"<userinput>3*4/2</userinput> returns 6."
msgstr ""
"Simboli zvezdice in poševnice izvajajo množenje in deljenje. &eg;, "
"<userinput>3*4/2</userinput> vrne 6."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:996
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>+</term>"
msgstr "<term> </term>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:997
#, no-c-format
msgid "&minus;"
msgstr "&minus;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:998
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The plus and minus symbols perform addition and subtraction. &eg;, "
"<userinput>1+3&minus;2</userinput> returns 2."
msgstr ""
"Simbola plus in minus izvajata seštevanje in odštevanje. &eg;, "
"<userinput>1+3&minus;2</userinput> vrne 2."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1004
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;"
msgstr "&lt;"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1005
#, no-c-format
msgid "&gt;"
msgstr "&gt;"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1006
#, no-c-format
msgid "&le;"
msgstr "&le;"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1007
#, no-c-format
msgid "&ge;"
msgstr "&ge;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1008
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Comparison operators. They return 1 if the expression is true, otherwise "
"they return 0. &eg;, <userinput>1 &le; 2</userinput> returns 1."
msgstr ""
"Operatorji primerjave. Vrnejo 1, če je izraz resničen, sicer vrnejo 0. &eg;, "
"<userinput>1 &le; 2</userinput> vrne 1."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1014
#, no-c-format
msgid "&radic;"
msgstr "&radic;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1015
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The square root of a number. &eg;, <userinput>&radic;4</userinput> returns 2."
msgstr "Kvadratni koren števila. &eg;, <userinput>&radic;4</userinput> vrne 2."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1021
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>|x|</term>"
msgstr "<term>|x|</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1022
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The absolute value of x. &eg;, <userinput>|&minus;4|</userinput> returns 4."
msgstr "Absolutna vrednost x. &eg;, <userinput>|&minus;4|</userinput> vrne 4."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1028
#, no-c-format
msgid "&plusmn;"
msgstr "&plusmn;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1030
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each plus-minus sign gives two sets of plots: one in which the plus is "
"taken, and one in which the minus is taken.&eg;. <userinput>y = &plusmn;"
"sqrt(1&minus;x^2)</userinput> will draw a circle. These, therefore, cannot "
"be used in constants."
msgstr ""
"Vsak znak plus-minus daje dva niza grafov: enega, v katerem je vzet plus, in "
"drugega, v katerem je vzet minus.&eg;. <userinput>y = &plusmn;sqrt(1&minus;"
"x^2)</userinput> bo narisal krog. Teh torej ni mogoče uporabiti v konstantah."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1040
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note the precedence, which means that if parentheses are not used, "
"exponentiation is performed before multiplication/division, which is "
"performed before addition/subtraction. So <userinput>1+2*4^2</userinput> "
"returns 33, and not, say 144. To override this, use parentheses. To use the "
"above example, <userinput>((1+2)*4)^2</userinput> <emphasis>will</emphasis> "
"return 144."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte prednost, kar pomeni, da če oklepaji niso uporabljeni, se "
"potenciranje izvede pred množenjem/deljenjem, ki se izvede pred seštevanjem/"
"odštevanjem. Torej <userinput>1+2*4^2</userinput> vrne 33 in ne recimo 144. "
"Če želite to preglasiti, uporabite oklepaje. Če želite uporabiti zgornji "
"primer, bo <userinput>((1+2)*4)^2</userinput> <emphasis></emphasis> vrnil "
"144."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1049
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plotting Area"
msgstr "Območje načrtovanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1050
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, explicitly given functions are plotted for the whole of the "
"visible part of the horizontal axis. You can specify an other range in the "
"edit-dialog for the function. If the plotting area contains the resulting "
"point it is connected to the last drawn point by a line."
msgstr ""
"Eksplicitno podane funkcije so privzeto izrisane za celoten vidni del "
"vodoravne osi. Za funkcijo lahko v pogovornem oknu za urejanje določite drug "
"obseg. Če območje risanja vsebuje nastalo točko, je povezana z zadnjo "
"narisano točko s črto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1056
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Parametric and polar functions have a default plotting range of 0 to 2&pgr;. "
"This plotting range can also be changed in the <guilabel>Functions</"
"guilabel> sidebar."
msgstr ""
"Parametrične in polarne funkcije imajo privzeto območje izrisa od 0 do "
"2&pgr;. Ta obseg izrisa lahko spremenite tudi v stranski vrstici "
"<guilabel>Funkcije</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1063
#, no-c-format
msgid "Crosshair Cursor"
msgstr "Kazalka s križcem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1064
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While the mouse cursor is over the plotting area the cursor changes to a "
"crosshair. The current coordinates can be seen at the intersections with the "
"coordinate axes and also in the status bar at the bottom of the main window."
msgstr ""
"Medtem ko je kazalka miške nad območjem risanja, se kazalka spremeni v "
"križec. Trenutne koordinate so vidne na sečiščih s koordinatnimi osemi in "
"tudi v statusni vrstici na dnu glavnega okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1067
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can trace a function's values more precisely by clicking onto or next to "
"a graph. The selected function is shown in the status bar in the right "
"column. The crosshair then will be caught and be colored in the same color "
"as the graph. If the graph has the same color as the background color, the "
"crosshair will have the inverted color of the background. When moving the "
"mouse or pressing the keys &Left; or &Right; the crosshair will follow the "
"function and you see the current horizontal and vertical value. If the "
"crosshair is close to vertical axis, the root-value is shown in the "
"statusbar. You can switch function with the &Up; and &Down; keys. A second "
"click anywhere in the window or pressing any non-navigating key will leave "
"this trace mode."
msgstr ""
"Vrednosti funkcije lahko natančneje sledite s klikom na graf ali poleg "
"njega. Izbrana funkcija je prikazana v vrstici stanja v desnem stolpcu. "
"Nitni križec bo nato ujet in obarvan v isto barvo kot graf. Če ima graf "
"enako barvo kot barva ozadja, bo imel križec obrnjeno barvo ozadja. Ko "
"premikate miško ali pritiskate tipke &Left; ali &Right; križec bo sledil "
"funkciji in videli boste trenutno vodoravno in navpično vrednost. Če je "
"križec blizu navpične osi, je korenska vrednost prikazana v vrstici stanja. "
"Funkcijo lahko preklopite s tipko &Up; in &Down; ključi. Drugi klik kjer "
"koli v oknu ali pritisk katere koli nenavigacijske tipke zapusti ta način "
"sledenja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1070
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more advanced tracing, open up the configuration dialog, and select "
"<guilabel>Draw tangent and normal when tracing</guilabel> from the "
"<guilabel>General Settings</guilabel> page. This option will draw the "
"tangent, normal and oscillating circle of the plot currently being traced."
msgstr ""
"Za bolj napredno sledenje odprite konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno in izberite "
"<guilabel>Nariši tangento in normalo pri sledenju</guilabel> na strani "
"<guilabel>Splošne nastavitve</guilabel>. Ta možnost bo narisala tangento, "
"normalo in nihajočo krožnico risbe, ki se trenutno sledi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1077
#, no-c-format
msgid "Coordinate System Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija koordinatnega sistema"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1078
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To open this dialog select <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Coordinate System...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from "
"the menubar."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odpreti to pogovorno okno, v menijski vrstici izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Koordinatni sistem ...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1080
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Screenshot of the Coordinate System dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna koordinatnega sistema</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1086
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Screenshot of the Coordinate System dialog</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna koordinatnega sistema</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1092
#, no-c-format
msgid "Axes Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija osi"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1097
#, no-c-format
msgid "Horizontal axis Range"
msgstr "Razpon vodoravne osi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1099
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the range for the horizontal axis scale. Note that you can use the "
"predefined functions and constants (see <xref linkend=\"func-predefined\"/>) "
"as the extremes of the range (&eg;, set <guilabel>Min:</guilabel> to "
"<userinput>2*pi</userinput>). You can even use functions you have defined to "
"set the extremes of the axis range. For example, if you have defined a "
"function <userinput>f(x) = x^2</userinput>, you could set <guilabel>Min:</"
"guilabel> to <userinput>f(3)</userinput>, which would make the lower end of "
"the range equal to 9."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi obseg za merilo vodoravne osi. Upoštevajte, da lahko uporabite "
"vnaprej določene funkcije in konstante (glejte <xref linkend=\"func-"
"predefined\"/>) kot skrajne vrednosti obsega (&eg; nastavite <guilabel>Min:</"
"guilabel> na <userinput>2* pi</userinput>). Uporabite lahko celo funkcije, "
"ki ste jih definirali, da nastavite skrajne vrednosti obsega osi. Na primer, "
"če ste definirali funkcijo <userinput>f(x) = x^2</userinput>, lahko "
"nastavite <guilabel>Min:</guilabel> na <userinput>f(3)</userinput>, zaradi "
"česar bi bila spodnja meja razpona enaka 9."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1112
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vertical axis Range"
msgstr "Razpon navpične osi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the range for the vertical axis. See <quote>Horizontal axis Range</"
"quote> above."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi obseg za navpično os. Glejte <quote>Razpon vodoravne osi</quote> "
"zgoraj."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1119
#, no-c-format
msgid "Horizontal axis Grid Spacing"
msgstr "Razmik mreže vodoravne osi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This controls the spacing between grid lines in the horizontal direction. If "
"<guilabel>Automatic</guilabel> is selected, then &kmplot; will try to find a "
"grid line spacing of about two centimeters that is also numerically nice. If "
"<guilabel>Custom:</guilabel> is selected, then you can enter the horizontal "
"grid spacing. This value will be used regardless of the zoom. For example, "
"if a value of 0.5 is entered, and the x range is 0 to 8, then 16 grid lines "
"will be shown."
msgstr ""
"To nadzira razmik med mrežnimi črtami v vodoravni smeri. Če je izbrano "
"<guilabel>Samodejno</guilabel>, potem &kmplot; bo poskušal najti razmik "
"mrežnih črt približno dva centimetra, ki je tudi številčno dober. Če je "
"izbrano <guilabel>Po meri:</guilabel>, lahko vnesete vodoravni razmik mreže. "
"Ta vrednost bo uporabljena ne glede na povečavo. Če je na primer vnesena "
"vrednost 0,5 in je obseg x od 0 do 8, bo prikazanih 16 mrežnih črt."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vertical axis Grid Spacing"
msgstr "Razmik mreže navpične osi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This controls the spacing between grid lines in the vertical direction. See "
"<quote>Horizontal axis Grid Spacing</quote> above."
msgstr ""
"To nadzoruje razmik med črtami mreže v navpični smeri. Glejte <quote>Razmik "
"mreže vodoravne osi</quote> zgoraj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1144
#, no-c-format
msgid "Constants Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija konstant"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To open this dialog select <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Constants...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the "
"menubar."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odpreti to pogovorno okno, izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konstante ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v menijski "
"vrstici."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1148
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Screenshot of the Constants dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna Konstante</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1154
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Screenshot of the Constants dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna Konstante</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Constants can be used as part of an expression anywhere inside of &kmplot;. "
"Each constant must have a name and a value. Some names are invalid, however, "
"such as existing function names or existing constants."
msgstr ""
"Konstante lahko uporabite kot del izraza kjer koli znotraj &kmplot;. Vsaka "
"konstanta mora imeti ime in vrednost. Nekatera imena pa so neveljavna, na "
"primer obstoječa imena funkcij ali obstoječe konstante."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1163
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are two options that control the scope of a constant:"
msgstr "Obstajata dve možnosti, ki nadzorujeta obseg konstante:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1169
#, no-c-format
msgid "Document"
msgstr "Dokument"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select the <guilabel>Document</guilabel> checkbox, then the Constant "
"will be saved along with the current diagram when you save it to file. "
"However, unless you have also selected the <guilabel>Global</guilabel> "
"option, the constant will not be available between instances of &kmplot;."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete potrditveno polje <guilabel>Dokument</guilabel>, bo konstanta "
"shranjena skupaj s trenutnim diagramom, ko jo shranite v datoteko. Vendar, "
"razen če ste izbrali tudi možnost <guilabel>Globalno</guilabel>, konstanta "
"ne bo na voljo med primerki &kmplot;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Global"
msgstr "Globalno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select the <guilabel>Global</guilabel> checkbox, then the Constant's "
"name and value will be written to &kde; settings (where it can also be used "
"by &kcalc;). The constant will not be lost when &kmplot; is closed, and will "
"be available again for use when &kmplot; is started again."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete potrditveno polje <guilabel>Globalno</guilabel>, bosta ime in "
"vrednost konstante zapisana v &kde; nastavitve (kjer ga lahko uporablja tudi "
"&kcalc;). Konstanta ne bo izgubljena, ko &kmplot; je zaprt in bo znova na "
"voljo za uporabo, ko &kmplot; se začne znova."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1190
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Reference"
msgstr "Referenca ukazov"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1193
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Items"
msgstr "Elementi menija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Apart from the common &kde; menus described in the <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/menus.html\">Menu</ulink> chapter of the &kde; Fundamentals "
"documentation &kmplot; has these application specific menu entries:"
msgstr ""
"Poleg običajnega &kde; meniji, opisani v poglavju <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/menus.html\">Meni</ulink> v &kde; Dokumentacija o osnovah "
"&kmplot; ima te menijske vnose za posamezne aplikacije:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1200
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr "Meni Datoteka"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1205
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Export...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izvoz ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Exports</action> the plotted graphs to an image file in all formats "
"supported by &kde;."
msgstr ""
"<action>Izvozi</action> izrisane grafe v slikovno datoteko v vseh formatih, "
"ki jih podpira &kde;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1212
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Natisni ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Opens</action> print configuration window. Press the "
"<guibutton>Options >></guibutton> button then choose the <guilabel>KmPlot "
"Options</guilabel> tab to configure options that are specific for &kmplot;."
msgstr ""
"<action>Odpre</action> okno za konfiguracijo tiskanja. Pritisnite gumb "
"<guibutton>Možnosti >></guibutton> in nato izberite zavihek "
"<guilabel>Možnosti KmPlot</guilabel>, da konfigurirate možnosti, ki so "
"specifične za &kmplot;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1223
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print Preview</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Predogled tiskanja</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Shows</action> the preliminary image of the current plot as printed "
"on the current default printer. Press the rightmost button on the toolbar of "
"the print preview window to configure options that are specific for &kmplot;."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaže</action> predhodno sliko trenutnega izrisa, kot je "
"natisnjena na trenutnem privzetem tiskalniku. Pritisnite skrajni desni gumb "
"v orodni vrstici okna za predogled tiskanja, da konfigurirate možnosti, ki "
"so specifične za &kmplot;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1236
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Edit Menu"
msgstr "Meni Urejanje"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1239
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Constants...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konstante ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays the <guilabel>Constants Editor</guilabel> dialog box. See <xref "
"linkend=\"constants-config\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže pogovorno okno <guilabel>Urejevalnik konstant</guilabel>. Glejte "
"<xref linkend=\"constants-config\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1249
#, no-c-format
msgid "The View Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1250
#, no-c-format
msgid "The first three items in the menu are related to zooming."
msgstr "Prvi trije elementi v meniju so povezani s povečavo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The mouse wheel can also be used as a zoom control. To zoom in or out using "
"the mouse, hold down the &Ctrl; key while you turn the mouse wheel. Each "
"tick increases or decreases the zoom factor by the value defined in the "
"<link linkend=\"general-config\">&kmplot; General settings</link>."
msgstr ""
"Kolesce miške lahko uporabite tudi kot nadzor povečave. Če želite z miško "
"povečati ali pomanjšati, pridržite &Ctrl; tipko, medtem ko vrtite kolesce "
"miške. Vsaka kljukica poveča ali zmanjša faktor povečave za vrednost, "
"določeno v <link linkend=\"general-config\">&kmplot; Splošne nastavitve</"
"link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>1</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zoom In</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>1</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Povečaj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tool can be operator in two different manners. To zoom in on a point on "
"the graph, click on it. To zoom in on a specific section of the graph, hold "
"and drag the mouse to form a rectangle, which will be the new axes ranges "
"when the mouse button is released."
msgstr ""
"To orodje lahko upravljate na dva različna načina. Če želite povečati točko "
"na grafu, kliknite nanjo. Če želite povečati določen odsek grafa, pridržite "
"in povlecite miško, da oblikujete pravokotnik, ki bo nova razpona osi, ko "
"spustite gumb miške."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>2</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zoom Out</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>2</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pomanjšaj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The tool can also be used in two different manners. To zoom out and center "
"on a point, click on that point. To fit the existing view into a rectangle, "
"hold and drag the mouse to form that rectangle."
msgstr ""
"Orodje se lahko uporablja tudi na dva različna načina. Za pomanjšanje in "
"centriranje točke kliknite to točko. Če želite obstoječi pogled prilagoditi "
"pravokotniku, pridržite in povlecite miško, da oblikujete ta pravokotnik."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Fit Widget to Trigonometric Functions</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prilagodi gradnik trigonometričnim "
"funkcijam</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The scale will be adapted to trigonometric functions. This works both for "
"radians and degrees."
msgstr ""
"Lestvica bo prilagojena trigonometričnim funkcijam. To deluje tako za "
"radiane kot stopinje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1298
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Reset View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ponastavi pogled</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1300
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resets the view."
msgstr "Ponastavi pogled."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1306
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Coordinate System...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Koordinatni sistem ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays the <guilabel>Coordinate System</guilabel> dialog box. See <xref "
"linkend=\"coords-config\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže pogovorno okno <guilabel>Koordinatni sistem</guilabel>. Glejte <xref "
"linkend=\"coords-config\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1314
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Sliders</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži drsnike</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1318
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Toggles</action> the visibility of the slider dialog. In the dialog "
"move a slider to change the parameter of the function plot connected to it."
msgstr ""
"<action>Preklopi</action> vidnost pogovornega okna drsnika. V pogovornem "
"oknu premaknite drsnik, da spremenite parameter grafa funkcije, ki je z njim "
"povezan."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable this on the Function tab and select one of the sliders to change the "
"parameter value dynamically. The values vary from 0 (left) to 10 (right) by "
"default, but can be changed in the slider dialog."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite to na zavihku Funkcija in izberite enega od drsnikov, da dinamično "
"spremenite vrednost parametra. Vrednosti se privzeto razlikujejo od 0 (levo) "
"do 10 (desno), vendar jih je mogoče spremeniti v pogovornem oknu drsnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1321
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For a small tutorial see <ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:"
"MyLanguage/KmPlot/Using_Sliders\">Using Sliders</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za majhno vadnico glejte <ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:"
"MyLanguage/KmPlot/Using_Sliders\">Uporaba drsnikov</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1331
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Tools Menu"
msgstr "Meni Orodja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1333
#, no-c-format
msgid "This menu contains some tools for the functions that can be useful:"
msgstr "Ta meni vsebuje nekaj orodij za funkcije, ki so lahko koristne:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1338
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Calculator</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kalkulator</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1347
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Plot Area...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Območje izrisa ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a graph and the values of the horizontal axis in the new dialog that "
"appears. Calculates the integral and draws the area between the graph and "
"the horizontal axis in the range of the selected values in the color of the "
"graph."
msgstr ""
"V novem pogovornem oknu, ki se prikaže, izberite graf in vrednosti vodoravne "
"osi. Izračuna integral in nariše območje med grafom in vodoravno osjo v "
"območju izbranih vrednosti v barvi grafa."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1358
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find Minimum...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Poišči minimum ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1362
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find the minimum value of the graph in a specified range."
msgstr "Poiščite najmanjšo vrednost grafa v določenem obsegu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1367
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find Maximum...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Poišči največ ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1371
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find the maximum value of the graph in a specified range."
msgstr "Poiščite največjo vrednost grafa v podanem območju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1379
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Help Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1381
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmplot; has a standard &kde; <guimenu>Help</guimenu> with one addition:"
msgstr ""
"&kmplot; ima standardni &kde; <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu> z enim dodatkom:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Predefined Math Functions...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prednastavljene matematične "
"funkcije ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1389
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens this handbook with a list of the predefined function names and "
"constants that &kmplot; knows."
msgstr ""
"Odpre ta priročnik s seznamom vnaprej določenih imen funkcij in konstant, ki "
"jih &kmplot; ve."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1401
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scripting &kmplot;"
msgstr "Skriptiranje &kmplot;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can write scripts for &kmplot; using &DBus;. For example, if you want to "
"define a new function <userinput>f(x)=2sin x+3cos x</userinput>, set its "
"line width to 20 and then draw it, you type in a console:"
msgstr ""
"Lahko pišete skripte za &kmplot; z &DBus;. Na primer, če želite definirati "
"novo funkcijo <userinput>f(x)=2sin x+3cos x</userinput>, nastaviti njeno "
"širino črte na 20 in jo nato narisati, v konzolo vnesete:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1404
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>qdbus org.kde.kmplot-PID /parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.addFunction "
"\"f(x)=2sin x+3cos x\" \"\"</command> As a result, the new function's id "
"number will be returned, or -1 if the function could not be defined."
msgstr ""
"<command>qdbus org.kde.kmplot-PID /parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.addFunction "
"\"f(x)=2sin x+3cos x\" \"\"</command> Posledično bo ID številka nove "
"funkcije ali -1, če funkcije ni bilo mogoče definirati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1406
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>qdbus org.kde.kmplot-PID /parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser."
"setFunctionFLineWidth ID 20</command> This command sets the function with "
"the id number ID the line width to 20."
msgstr ""
"<command>qdbus org.kde.kmplot-PID /parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser."
"setFunctionFLineWidth ID 20</command> Ta ukaz nastavi funkcijo z ID številko "
"ID širino vrstice na 20."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>qdbus org.kde.kmplot-PID /view org.kde.kmplot.View.drawPlot</"
"command> This command repaints the window so that the function get visible."
msgstr ""
"<command>qdbus org.kde.kmplot-PID /view org.kde.kmplot.View.drawPlot</"
"command> Ta ukaz prebarva okno, tako da postane funkcija vidna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1410
#, no-c-format
msgid "A list of the available functions:"
msgstr "Seznam razpoložljivih funkcij:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1414
#, no-c-format
msgid "/kmplot org.kde.kmplot.KmPlot.fileOpen url"
msgstr "/kmplot org.kde.kmplot.KmPlot.fileOdpri url"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1418
#, no-c-format
msgid "Load the file <parameter>url</parameter>."
msgstr "Naloži datoteko <parameter>url</parameter>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1422
#, no-c-format
msgid "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.isModified"
msgstr "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.isModified"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1426
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns true if any changes are done."
msgstr "Vrne true, če so bile izvedene kakršne koli spremembe."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1430
#, no-c-format
msgid "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.checkModified"
msgstr "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.checkModified"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If there are any unsaved changes, a dialog appears to save, discard or "
"cancel the plots."
msgstr ""
"Če obstajajo neshranjene spremembe, se prikaže pogovorno okno za "
"shranjevanje, zavrženje ali preklic izrisov."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1438
#, no-c-format
msgid "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.editAxes"
msgstr "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.editAxes"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1442
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the coordinate system edit dialog."
msgstr "Odpre pogovorno okno za urejanje koordinatnega sistema."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1446
#, no-c-format
msgid "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.toggleShowSlider"
msgstr "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.toggleShowSlider"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1450
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows/hides parameter slider window."
msgstr "Prikaže/skrije okno drsnika parametrov."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1454
#, no-c-format
msgid "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.slotSave"
msgstr "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.slotSave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1458
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saves the functions (opens the save dialog if it is a new file)."
msgstr ""
"Shrani funkcije (odpre pogovorno okno za shranjevanje, če gre za novo "
"datoteko)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1462
#, no-c-format
msgid "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.slotSaveas"
msgstr "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.slotSaveas"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1466
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The same as choosing the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Save As...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the menu."
msgstr ""
"Enako kot če bi v meniju izbrali <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani kot...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1470
#, no-c-format
msgid "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.slotPrint"
msgstr "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.slotPrint"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1474
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the print dialog."
msgstr "Odpre pogovorno okno za tiskanje."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1478
#, no-c-format
msgid "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.slotResetView"
msgstr "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.slotResetView"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1482
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The same as choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Reset "
"View</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the menu."
msgstr ""
"Enako kot bi v meniju izbrali <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Ponastavi pogled</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1486
#, no-c-format
msgid "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.slotExport"
msgstr "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.slotExport"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1490
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the export dialog."
msgstr "Odpre pogovorno okno za izvoz."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1494
#, no-c-format
msgid "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.slotSettings"
msgstr "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.slotSettings"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1498
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the settings dialog."
msgstr "Odpre pogovorno okno z nastavitvami."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1502
#, no-c-format
msgid "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.slotNames"
msgstr "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.slotNames"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1506
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows the predefined math functions in the handbook."
msgstr "Prikaže vnaprej določene matematične funkcije v priročniku."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1510
#, no-c-format
msgid "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.findMinimumValue"
msgstr "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.findMinimumValue"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1514
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The same as choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Minimum Value...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the menu."
msgstr ""
"Enako kot če bi v meniju izbrali <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Najmanjša vrednost ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1518
#, no-c-format
msgid "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.findMaximumValue"
msgstr "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.findMaximumValue"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1522
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The same as choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Maximum Value...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the menu."
msgstr ""
"Enako kot če bi v meniju izbrali <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Največja vrednost ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1526
#, no-c-format
msgid "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.graphArea"
msgstr "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.graphArea"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1530
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The same as choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Plot "
"Area...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the menu."
msgstr ""
"Enako kot če bi v meniju izbrali <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Območje izrisa ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1534
#, no-c-format
msgid "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.calculator"
msgstr "/maindlg org.kde.kmplot.MainDlg.calculator"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1538
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The same as choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Calculator</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the menu."
msgstr ""
"Enako kot če bi v meniju izbrali <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Kalkulator</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1542
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.addFunction f_str0 f_fstr1"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.addFunction f_str0 f_fstr1"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1546
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adds a new function with the expressions <parameter>f_str0</parameter> and "
"<parameter>f_str1</parameter>. If the expression does not contain a function "
"name, it will be auto-generated. The id number of the new function is "
"returned, or -1 if the function could not be defined."
msgstr ""
"Doda novo funkcijo z izrazoma <parameter>f_str0</parameter> in "
"<parameter>f_str1</parameter>. Če izraz ne vsebuje imena funkcije, bo "
"samodejno ustvarjen. Vrne se ID številka nove funkcije ali -1, če funkcije "
"ni bilo mogoče definirati."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1550
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.removeFunction id"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.removeFunction id"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1554
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Removes the function with the id number <parameter>id</parameter>. If the "
"function could not be deleted, false is returned, otherwise true."
msgstr ""
"Odstrani funkcijo z ID številko <parameter>id</parameter>. Če funkcije ni "
"bilo mogoče izbrisati, je vrnjena vrednost false, sicer pa vrednost true."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1558
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.setFunctionExpression id eq f_str"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.setFunctionExpression id eq f_str"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1562
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the expression for the function with the id number <parameter>id</"
"parameter> to <parameter>f_str</parameter>. Returns true if it succeed, "
"otherwise false."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi izraz za funkcijo s številko ID <parameter>id</parameter> na "
"<parameter>f_str</parameter>. Vrne true, če je uspešen, sicer false."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1566
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.countFunctions"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.countFunctions"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1570
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the number of functions (parametric functions are calculated as two)."
msgstr "Vrne število funkcij (parametrične funkcije se izračunajo kot dve)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1575
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.listFunctionNames"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.listFunctionNames"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1579
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns a list with all functions."
msgstr "Vrne seznam z vsemi funkcijami."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1583
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.fnameToID f_str"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.fnameToID f_str"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1587
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the id number of <parameter>f_str</parameter> or -1 if the function "
"name <parameter>f_str</parameter> was not found."
msgstr ""
"Vrne številko id <parameter>f_str</parameter> ali -1, če ime funkcije "
"<parameter>f_str</parameter> ni bilo najdeno."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1591
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionFVisible id"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionFVisible id"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1595
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns true if the function with the ID <parameter>id</parameter> is "
"visible, otherwise false."
msgstr ""
"Vrne true, če je funkcija z ID-jem <parameter>id</parameter> vidna, sicer "
"false."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1599
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionF1Visible id"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionF1Viden id"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1603
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns true if the first derivative of the function with the ID "
"<parameter>id</parameter> is visible, otherwise false."
msgstr ""
"Vrne true, če je vidna prva izpeljanka funkcije z ID-jem <parameter>id</"
"parameter>, sicer false."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1607
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionF2Visible id"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionF2Viden id"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1611
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns true if the second derivative of the function with the ID "
"<parameter>id</parameter> is visible, otherwise false."
msgstr ""
"Vrne true, če je vidna druga izpeljanka funkcije z ID-jem <parameter>id</"
"parameter>, sicer pa false."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1615
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionIntVisible id"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionIntVisible id"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1619
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns true if the integral of the function with the ID <parameter>id</"
"parameter> is visible, otherwise false."
msgstr ""
"Vrne true, če je integral funkcije z ID-jem <parameter>id</parameter> viden, "
"sicer false."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1623
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.setFunctionFVisible id visible"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.setFunctionFVisible ID viden"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1627
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows the function with the ID <parameter>id</parameter> if "
"<parameter>visible</parameter> is true. If <parameter>visible</parameter> is "
"false, the function will be hidden. True is returned if the function exists, "
"otherwise false."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže funkcijo z ID-jem <parameter>id</parameter>, če je <parameter>viden</"
"parameter> resničen. Če je <parameter>viden</parameter> nastavljen na false, "
"bo funkcija skrita. Če funkcija obstaja, se vrne vrednost True, sicer pa "
"vrednost false."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1631
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.setFunctionF1Visible id visible"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.setFunctionF1Visible ID viden"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1635
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows the first derivative of the function with the ID <parameter>id</"
"parameter> if <parameter>visible</parameter> is true. If <parameter>visible</"
"parameter> is false, the function will be hidden. True is returned if the "
"function exists, otherwise false."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže prvo izpeljanko funkcije z ID-jem <parameter>id</parameter>, če je "
"<parameter>viden</parameter> resničen. Če je <parameter>viden</parameter> "
"nastavljen na false, bo funkcija skrita. Če funkcija obstaja, se vrne "
"vrednost True, sicer pa vrednost false."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1639
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.setFunctionF2Visible id visible"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.setFunctionF2Visible ID viden"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1643
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows the second derivative of the function with the ID <parameter>id</"
"parameter> if <parameter>visible</parameter> is true. If <parameter>visible</"
"parameter> is false, the function will be hidden. True is returned if the "
"function exists, otherwise false."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže drugo izpeljanko funkcije z ID-jem <parameter>id</parameter>, če je "
"<parameter>viden</parameter> resničen. Če je <parameter>viden</parameter> "
"nastavljen na false, bo funkcija skrita. Če funkcija obstaja, se vrne "
"vrednost True, sicer pa vrednost false."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1647
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.setFunctionIntVisible id visible"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.setFunctionIntVisible ID viden"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1651
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows the integral of the function with the ID <parameter>id</parameter> if "
"<parameter>visible</parameter> is true. If <parameter>visible</parameter> is "
"false, the function will be hidden. True is returned if the function exists, "
"otherwise false."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže integral funkcije z ID-jem <parameter>id</parameter>, če je "
"<parameter>viden</parameter> resničen. Če je <parameter>viden</parameter> "
"nastavljen na false, bo funkcija skrita. Če funkcija obstaja, se vrne "
"vrednost True, sicer pa vrednost false."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1655
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionStr id eq"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionStr id eq"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1659
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the function expression of the function with the ID <parameter>id</"
"parameter>. If the function not exists, an empty string is returned instead."
msgstr ""
"Vrne funkcijski izraz funkcije z ID-jem <parameter>id</parameter>. Če "
"funkcija ne obstaja, se vrne prazen niz."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1663
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionFLineWidth id"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionFLineWidth id"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1667
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the line width of the function with the ID <parameter>id</"
"parameter>. If the function not exists, 0 is returned."
msgstr ""
"Vrne širino vrstice funkcije z ID-jem <parameter>id</parameter>. Če funkcija "
"ne obstaja, se vrne 0."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1671
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionF1LineWidth id"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionF1LineWidth id"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1675
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the line width of the first derivative of the function with the ID "
"<parameter>id</parameter>. If the function not exists, 0 is returned."
msgstr ""
"Vrne širino črte prve izpeljanke funkcije z ID-jem <parameter>id</"
"parameter>. Če funkcija ne obstaja, se vrne 0."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1679
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionF2LineWidth id"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionF2LineWidth id"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the line width of the second derivative of the function with the ID "
"<parameter>id</parameter>. If the function not exists, 0 is returned."
msgstr ""
"Vrne širino črte druge izpeljanke funkcije z ID-jem <parameter>id</"
"parameter>. Če funkcija ne obstaja, se vrne 0."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1687
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionIntLineWidth id"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionIntLineWidth id"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1691
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the line width of the integral of the function with the ID "
"<parameter>id</parameter>. If the function not exists, 0 is returned."
msgstr ""
"Vrne širino črte integrala funkcije z ID-jem <parameter>id</parameter>. Če "
"funkcija ne obstaja, se vrne 0."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1695
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.setFunctionFLineWidth id linewidth"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.setFunctionFLineWidth id širina vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1699
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the line width of the function with the ID <parameter>id</parameter> to "
"<parameter>linewidth</parameter>. True is returned if the function exists, "
"otherwise false."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi širino črte funkcije z ID-jem <parameter>id</parameter> na "
"<parameter>širina črte</parameter>. Če funkcija obstaja, se vrne vrednost "
"True, sicer pa vrednost false."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1703
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.setFunctionF1LineWidth id linewidth"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.setFunctionF1LineWidth id širina vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1707
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the line width of the first derivative of the function with the ID "
"<parameter>id</parameter> to <parameter>linewidth</parameter>. True is "
"returned if the function exists, otherwise false."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi širino črte prve izpeljanke funkcije z ID-jem <parameter>id</"
"parameter> na <parameter>širina črte</parameter>. Če funkcija obstaja, se "
"vrne vrednost True, sicer pa vrednost false."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1711
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.setFunctionF2LineWidth id linewidth"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.setFunctionF2LineWidth id širina vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1715
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the line width of the second derivative of the function with the ID "
"<parameter>id</parameter> to <parameter>linewidth</parameter>. True is "
"returned if the function exists, otherwise false."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi širino črte druge izpeljanke funkcije z ID-jem <parameter>id</"
"parameter> na <parameter>širina črte</parameter>. Če funkcija obstaja, se "
"vrne vrednost True, sicer pa vrednost false."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1719
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.setFunctionIntLineWidth id linewidth"
msgstr ""
"/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.setFunctionIntLineWidth id širina vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1723
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the line width of the integral of the function with the ID "
"<parameter>id</parameter> to <parameter>linewidth</parameter>. True is "
"returned if the function exists, otherwise false."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi širino črte integrala funkcije z ID-jem <parameter>id</parameter> na "
"<parameter>širina črte</parameter>. Če funkcija obstaja, se vrne vrednost "
"True, sicer pa vrednost false."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1727
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionParameterList id"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionParameterList id"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1731
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns a list with all the parameter values for the function with the ID "
"<parameter>id</parameter>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne seznam z vsemi vrednostmi parametrov za funkcijo z ID-jem "
"<parameter>id</parameter>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1735
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionAddParameter id new_parameter"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionAddParameter id nov_parameter"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1739
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adds the parameter value <parameter>new_parameter</parameter> to the "
"function with the ID <parameter>id</parameter>. True is returned if the "
"operation succeed, otherwise false."
msgstr ""
"Doda vrednost parametra <parameter>nov_parameter</parameter> funkciji z ID-"
"jem <parameter>id</parameter>. Če je operacija uspešna, se vrne True, sicer "
"pa false."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1743
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionRemoveParameter id remove_parameter"
msgstr ""
"/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionRemoveParameter id remove_parameter"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1747
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Removes the parameter value <parameter>remove_parameter</parameter> from the "
"function with the ID <parameter>id</parameter>. True is returned if the "
"operation succeed, otherwise false."
msgstr ""
"Odstrani vrednost parametra <parameter>odstrani_parameter</parameter> iz "
"funkcije z ID-jem <parameter>id</parameter>. Če je operacija uspešna, se "
"vrne True, sicer pa false."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1751
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionMinValue id"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionMinValue id"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1755
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the minimum plot range value of the function with the ID "
"<parameter>id</parameter>. If the function not exists or if the minimum "
"value is not defined, an empty string is returned."
msgstr ""
"Vrne najmanjšo vrednost obsega izrisa funkcije z ID-jem <parameter>id</"
"parameter>. Če funkcija ne obstaja ali če najmanjša vrednost ni definirana, "
"se vrne prazen niz."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1759
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionMaxValue id"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionMaxValue id"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1763
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the maximum plot range value of the function with the ID "
"<parameter>id</parameter>. If the function not exists or if the maximum "
"value is not defined, an empty string is returned."
msgstr ""
"Vrne največjo vrednost obsega izrisa funkcije z ID-jem <parameter>id</"
"parameter>. Če funkcija ne obstaja ali če največja vrednost ni definirana, "
"se vrne prazen niz."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1767
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.setFunctionMinValue id min"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.setFunctionMinValue id min"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1771
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the minimum plot range value of the function with the ID <parameter>id</"
"parameter> to <parameter>min</parameter>. True is returned if the function "
"exists and the expression is valid, otherwise false."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi najmanjšo vrednost obsega izrisa funkcije z ID-jem <parameter>id</"
"parameter> na <parameter>min</parameter>. True je vrnjen, če funkcija "
"obstaja in je izraz veljaven, sicer pa false."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1775
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.setFunctionMaxValue id max"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.setFunctionMaxValue id max"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1779
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the maximum plot range value of the function with the ID <parameter>id</"
"parameter> to <parameter>max</parameter>. True is returned if the function "
"exists and the expression is valid, otherwise false."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi največjo vrednost obsega izrisa funkcije z ID-jem <parameter>id</"
"parameter> na <parameter>max</parameter>. True je vrnjen, če funkcija "
"obstaja in je izraz veljaven, sicer pa false."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1784
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionStartXValue id"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionStartXValue id"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1788
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the initial x point for the integral of the function with the ID "
"<parameter>id</parameter>. If the function not exists or if the x-point-"
"expression is not defined, an empty string is returned."
msgstr ""
"Vrne začetno točko x za integral funkcije z ID-jem <parameter>id</"
"parameter>. Če funkcija ne obstaja ali če izraz točke x ni definiran, je "
"vrnjen prazen niz."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1792
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionStartYValue id"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.functionStartYValue id"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1796
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the initial y point for the integral of the function with the ID "
"<parameter>id</parameter>. If the function not exists or if the y-point-"
"expression is not defined, an empty string is returned."
msgstr ""
"Vrne začetno točko y za integral funkcije z ID-jem <parameter>id</"
"parameter>. Če funkcija ne obstaja ali če izraz točke y ni definiran, je "
"vrnjen prazen niz."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1800
#, no-c-format
msgid "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.setFunctionStartValue id x y"
msgstr "/parser org.kde.kmplot.Parser.setFunctionStartValue id x y"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1804
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the initial x and y point for the integral of the function with the ID "
"<parameter>id</parameter> to <parameter>x</parameter> and <parameter>y</"
"parameter>. True is returned if the function exists and the expression is "
"valid, otherwise false."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi začetno točko x in y za integral funkcije z ID-jem <parameter>id</"
"parameter> na <parameter>x</parameter> in <parameter>y</parameter>. True je "
"vrnjen, če funkcija obstaja in je izraz veljaven, sicer pa false."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1808
#, no-c-format
msgid "/view org.kde.kmplot.View.stopDrawing"
msgstr "/view org.kde.kmplot.View.stopDrawing"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1812
#, no-c-format
msgid "If &kmplot; currently is drawing a function, the procedure will stop."
msgstr "Če &kmplot; trenutno riše funkcijo, postopek se bo ustavil."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1816
#, no-c-format
msgid "/view org.kde.kmplot.View.drawPlot"
msgstr "/view org.kde.kmplot.View.drawPlot"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1820
#, no-c-format
msgid "Redraws all functions."
msgstr "Ponovno nariše vse funkcije."

